SetShd.name: SetShd
SetShd.description: Specify the shading which shall be applied to the extents of the current table cell.

SetCellMarginBottom.name: SetCellMarginBottom
SetCellMarginBottom.description:
Specifies the amount of space which shall be left between the bottom extent of the cell contents and the border
of a specific table cell within a table.

params.name: nValue
params.description:
If this value is null, then default table cell bottom margin shall be used,
otherwise override the table cell bottom margin with specified value for the current cell.

SetCellMarginLeft.name: SetCellMarginLeft
SetCellMarginLeft.description:
Specifies the amount of space which shall be left between the left extent of the current cell contents and the
left edge border of a specific individual table cell within a table.

params.name: nValue
params.description:
If this value is null, then default table cell bottom margin shall be used,
otherwise override the table cell bottom margin with specified value for the current cell.

SetCellMarginRight.name: SetCellMarginRight
SetCellMarginRight.description:
Specifies the amount of space which shall be left between the right extent of the current cell contents and the
right edge border of a specific individual table cell within a table.

params.name: nValue
params.description:
If this value is null, then default table cell bottom margin shall be used,
otherwise override the table cell bottom margin with specified value for the current cell.

SetCellMarginTop.name: SetCellMarginTop
SetCellMarginTop.description:
Specifies the amount of space which shall be left between the top extent of the current cell contents and the
top edge border of a specific individual table cell within a table.

params.name: nValue
params.description:
If this value is null, then default table cell bottom margin shall be used,
otherwise override the table cell bottom margin with specified value for the current cell.

SetCellBorderBottom.name: SetCellBorderBottom
SetCellBorderBottom.description: Set the border which shall be displayed at the bottom of the current table cell.

SetCellBorderLeft.name: SetCellBorderLeft
SetCellBorderLeft.description: Set the border which shall be displayed at the left of the current table cell.

SetCellBorderRight.name: SetCellBorderRight
SetCellBorderRight.description: Set the border which shall be displayed at the right of the current table cell.

SetCellBorderTop.name: SetCellBorderTop
SetCellBorderTop.description: Set the border which shall be displayed at the top of the current table cell.

SetVerticalAlign.name: SetVerticalAlign
SetVerticalAlign.description: Specify the vertical alignment for text within the current table cell.

SetTextDirection.name: SetTextDirection
SetTextDirection.description: Specify the direction of the text flow for this table cell.
